{"tid":1020694,"cid":21,"subCid":2,"title":"情人節勾起那段回憶 - 安靜 (原唱:周杰倫) Piano Cover","createTime":"2019-02-13T19:01:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-17T03:53:11.000Z","uid":190992,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8868646862f74ac5959089005f983dac269a2f3f","tid":1020694,"uid":190992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T19:01:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nx8x9-qxPxA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dnx8x9-qxPxA&d=uNZXw00WsTXXX%2FAwV3JyEQ1nSF4GOVyTVdrqrZ1TEh8%3D&h=c45bbb4b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nx8x9-qxPxA</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/jfM9fvB/silent-snapshot-1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ibb.co%2FjfM9fvB%2Fsilent-snapshot-1.png&h=e259619c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n情人節勾起那段回憶 - 安靜 (原唱:周杰倫) Piano Cover by 夢詞人<br />\n<br />\n只剩下鋼琴陪我彈了一天<br />\n睡著的大提琴　安靜的舊舊的<br />\n我想你已表現的非常明白<br />\n我懂我也知道　你沒有捨不得<br />\n<br />\n你說你也會難過我不相信<br />\n牽著你陪著我　也只是曾經<br />\n希望他是真的比我還要愛你<br />\n我才會逼自己離開<br />\n<br />\n你要我說多難堪　我根本不想分開<br />\n為什麼還要我用微笑來帶過<br />\n我沒有這種天份　包容你也接受他<br />\n不用擔心的太多　我會一直好好過<br />\n你已經遠遠離開　我也會慢慢走開<br />\n為什麼我連分開都遷就著你<br />\n我真的沒有天份　安靜的沒這麼快<br />\n我會學著放棄你　是因為我太愛你<br />\n<br />\n#安靜,#周杰倫,#新詞,#改編,#粵語歌,#勵志歌,#我的推介,#廣東歌,#歌詞,#音樂,#唱作人,#填詞人,#香港音樂,#創作,#原創音樂,#香港原創,#cantopop,#music,#song,#songs,#popmusic,#hk,#hongkong,#hkmusic,#hongkongmusic"},{"pid":"bdc6191733c66dcab853b3c5f70aeb8ef834005d","tid":1020694,"uid":190992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T17:23:59.000Z","msg":"連周董o既都就快二十年, 真係歲月如梭"},{"pid":"9cd5946841c89ee9ead7f0eebd47d253279e2efb","tid":1020694,"uid":190992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T17:25:10.000Z","msg":"*日月如梭"},{"pid":"8ed352f159740855898500f0f631ba874273e0e6","tid":1020694,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T03:53:11.000Z","msg":"<img src